,"quote":{"pid":"27768d11e555cfe1f0f8d7cb309dbe56402be802","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:22:51.000Z","msg":"點解有d人咁反感有死後的世界去繼續受報呢？？<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔係唔信簡單，佢地直程係極度厭惡&ldquo;死後繼續受報&rdquo;呢個根念，甚至恨之入骨<br />\n<br />\n點解？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"但明明佢地幾年前的仇人，今日已經係另一堆粒子聚合物（可以咁睇，當幾年前那個仇人已經被原子彈炸到氣化了），但佢地死都要仇恨同報復在另一堆完全唔同的粒子聚合物身上，何不找回失去了的粒子，再砌積木咁組合番，再報仇在那個積木人身上呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然今日的某人同幾年前的某人，不是同一件&ldquo;物體&rdquo;，咁點解法律要因為某人幾年前的罪行而懲罰今日的某人呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2342838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2342838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"因為靈魂都係同一個嚟？"},{"pid":"5e31fe2a75afe7c313781b9af90ba4f6ecf65ccf","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06a731684815df8eb5c3ea5e3efdcffb3e8adf5","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b7d678edc7c0b872f6977740c6faa11b2425c1","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88455185cd57ad42f43a5aaf4c7433ca74b17bd6","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68e7c92058ec4ce8bce958d9b5bb6c588709157","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HUgZ7kztPBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHUgZ7kztPBs&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=3fc4ac84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HUgZ7kztPBs</a>"},{"pid":"c85a52cf4011952122f6055dea30073da29f39cc","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a44e6db87c787e19d6009f9c2b4fe0b91063fe","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T01:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1440b57ad1dabfd268f7469087389a999eb84c6","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8bccffccad186451d43aad5571eb85df2a3988","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f701c5c45df10ab9a6397c392f242b9b96d1add","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fa1604702a74b0e02e2b83a8e193f6af3f08d6d","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf82d43f9d9488adaf05652e66de6f9a389433b0","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a134253d53c39b4228fa02dfcd00b93eec2890aa","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T01:58:21.000Z","msg":"另一個睇法，基於人體粒子的替換，幾年前的自己已死掉（當被原子彈炸到氣化了），今日的自己亦在幾年後死掉（當被原子彈炸到氣化了）<br />\n<br />\nloop loop loop.....<br />\n<br />\n人在老去的日子，可能真的有原子彈或其他大威力炸彈把自己炸到氣化了，情況亦如是<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼人怕原子彈轟炸呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"假設（如有雷同實屬巧合）：<br />\n<br />\n在人真的被原子彈轟炸氣化了之後，或不是氣化，而是血肉橫飛，在滿地的殘肢血肉上，有一隻屍蟲初長出，那麼可能這屍蟲亦擔心自己被原子彈氣化，不過其實屍蟲又不斷經歷身體粒子的偽氣化looping<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nloop loop loop<br />\n<br />\n那麼在上文所有的真氣化同偽氣化的looping中，有甚麼&ldquo;本質&rdquo;去貫穿那些完全不同的身體呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"關於美國有錢佬之進退兩難，他們要在世永生就要靠科學，但科研卻毀滅他們在世永生的希望<br />\n<br />\n例如：人體粒子替換的揭露，也就代表其實自己不斷被&ldquo;偽氣化&rdquo;，也就是說，他們現在食一粒原子彈並且真的氣化了，也是好平常的事，不足為懼<br />\n<br />\n當然，他們可以叫手下幫自己找回粒子，再砌番自出黎繼續喎<br />\n<br />\n如何辦呢？手下懷孕就可以了<br />\n<br />\n如此，又開始&ldquo;身體粒子替換的偽氣化&rdquo;同&ldquo;原爆真氣化&rdquo;的最後結果，又再loop<br />\n<br />\nloop loop loop.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我稱之為&ldquo;霍金困局&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fh8aJAPPIHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFh8aJAPPIHY&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=4985ee5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fh8aJAPPIHY</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R_2f01O_A4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR_2f01O_A4s&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=8d9549fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R_2f01O_A4s</a>"},{"pid":"b9427c880e748265b8521ac76de6263f3a00b0e8","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16523c6b9ad398b2cbfef47f2941aefab0945e5","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26dcd79f0fa2ca9f1dec084e6899b13b64a16d5","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c795af24ca6e7941390f1e701cd68b2e23de5d60","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9aa923f7385132a949b568b5c51b67dc42b4fe","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d359037fab8c8110ab1b8fbf7c7039538fc23d40","tid":2452571,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}